{"type":"message","id":"caef8dab","parentId":"d9d0b67d","timestamp":"2026-04-25T07:39:56.555Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze each task:\n\n1. `investment-research-background-overnight-2100` - `cron 0 21 * * *` - every day at 21:00, no weekday restriction. This is the overnight/night duty task. It runs every day.\n\n2. `08:50全球股市早间要闻` - `cron 50 8 * * *` - every day at 08:50, no weekday restriction. This should be restricted to trading days (1-5).\n\n3. `每日16:00 dual factor c...` - `cron 0 16 * * 1-5` - Monday to Friday, already OK.\n\n\n4. `16:30 生成量化面板总入口` - `cron 30 16 * * 1-5` - Monday to Friday, already OK.\n5. `16:30来福投研会-盘后值班` - `cron 30 16 * * 1-5` - Monday to Friday, already OK.\n6. `17:00 A股ML预测每日更新` - `cron 0 17 * * 1-5` - Monday to Friday, already OK.\n\nSo the two tasks that need weekday restrictions are the overnight background research at 21:00 and the morning global market news briefing at 08:50, both currently running every day without any trading day filtering.\n\nThe morning report is particularly problematic since weekends and holidays have no market activity, and the overnight task probably won't have relevant content to generate either. I should present this to the user and ask if they want me to restrict both to weekdays only.","thinkingSignature":"2aaf555bf0225a775724b0972abf3a679e9be8c6cd580d0dd7ff9e0e94249e8d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n经过逐个检查，结论如下：\n\n**✅ 已加交易日限制（无问题）：**\n- `每日16:00 dual factor c...` — `1-5` 周一至周五\n- `16:30 生成量化面板总入口` — `1-5`\n- `16:30来福投研会-盘后值班` — `1-5`\n- `17:00 A股ML预测每日更新` — `1-5`\n- 几个盘中值班任务 — 都是 `1-5`\n\n**⚠️ 需修复（没加交易日限制，每天都跑）：**\n\n| 任务 | 问题 |\n|------|------|\n| `08:50全球股市早间要闻` | 非交易日无交易数据，推了也没用 |\n| `21:00来福投研会-夜间值班` | 夜间值班非交易日意义不大 |\n\n需要我把这两个也改成 `1-5` 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":491,"output":536,"cacheRead":42240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43267,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRea