{"type":"message","id":"ef536a34","parentId":"3d103fcc","timestamp":"2026-04-25T07:42:45.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Neither has node_modules. I'll need to install them. Let me now plan the full configuration:\n\n1. Create a desktop-specific config directory (separate from the integrated quant system)\n2. The user wants a \"desktop edition\" - this means a standalone Electron app\n3. For macOS, the full build requires:\n   - Build React UI (`apps/dsa-web`)\n   - Build backend with PyInstaller (`scripts/build-backend-macos.sh`)\n   - Build Electron app (`scripts/build-desktop-macos.sh`)\n\nThe main consideration is that Electron is not installed (`which electron` returned not found). I need to install it.\n\nLet me first ask the user for clarification on what they want specifically, since:\n\n\n- They mentioned this repo is \"already integrated into their quant investment system\"\n- They want a \"separate desktop version\"\n\nSo they probably want to use the same codebase but build a standalone desktop app. Let me confirm what configuration they want - like what STOCK_LIST they'll use, which notification channels to enable, and what AI model they prefer.\n\nActually, looking at the docs, the user needs to edit the `.env` file with their API key and stock list, so I should ask them about that. But they said \"帮我配置吧\" (help me configure), which means they want me to set it up. The most logical thing is to set up a separate local `.env` file for the desktop edition. Since this is running on macOS with Apple Silicon (M1/M2), I need to make sure the build targets arm64.\n\nI should ask the user 3 key questions: what stock list they want to monitor, what AI model they prefer, and what notification channels they want to use. But I have the `feishu_ask_user_question` tool available, so I can use that to interact with them. Actually, the most efficient approach might be to check if there's a default `.env.example` that already has some reasonable defaults and build from there, rather than asking too many questions upfront.\n\nLet me figure out what's already in the `.env.example` so I can give them a sensible starting point.","thinkingSignature":"c6e699ff87520aca028e24166683d6cddefa130cbe9a3ec56ea833f7bdb5adc0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8jykoauseqt3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -80 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/.env.example"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":138,"output":479,"cacheRead":62048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777102950594,"responseId":"063ba3660ffbd64637c72bb8cc7881bc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f05ecfa9","parentId":"ef536a34","timestamp":"2026-04-25T07:42:45.481Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8jykoauseqt3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ===================================\n# A股自选股智能分析系统 - 环境变量配置模板\n# 复制此文件为 .env 并填入真实配置\n# ===================================\n\n# 自选股列表（逗号分隔，支持沪深两市代码）\n# 沪市：600xxx, 601xxx, 603xxx\n# 深市：000xxx, 002xxx, 300xxx\nSTOCK_LIST=600519,300750,002594\n\n# 数据源配置\n# Tushare Pro Token（可选，从 https://tushare.pro/weborder/#/login?reg=834638 获取）\nTUSHARE_TOKEN=\n# TickFlow API Key（可选，用于 A 股大盘复盘指数增强；若套餐支持标的池查询，也可增强市场统计）\n# TICKFLOW_API_KEY=\n# Longbridge OpenAPI（可选，美股/港股量比、换手率、PE 等字段兜底）\n# 从 https://open.longbridge.com/ 获取\n# LONGBRIDGE_APP_KEY=\n# LONGBRIDGE_APP_SECRET=\n# LONGBRIDGE_ACCESS_TOKEN=\n# static_info 进程内缓存秒数，默认 86400；0=每次请求拉取\n# LONGBRIDGE_STATIC_INFO_TTL_SECONDS=86400\n# Longbridge SDK 语言与 REPORT_LANGUAGE（zh/en）一致；SDK 日志写入 LOG_DIR/longbridge_sdk.log\n# 接入点（与 REPORT_LANGUAGE 无关；留空则用下列默认值）：\n# LONGBRIDGE_HTTP_URL=https://openapi.longbridge.com\n# LONGBRIDGE_QUOTE_WS_URL=wss://openapi-quote.longbridge.com/v2\n# LONGBRIDGE_TRADE_WS_URL=wss://openapi-trade.longbridge.com/v2\n# LONGBRIDGE_REGION=hk\n# 覆盖接入点；SDK 内部用 LONGPORT_REGION（不带 BRIDGE）自动选择，\n# 代码会自动同步 LONGBRIDGE_REGION → LONGPORT_REGION。\n# hk → *.longbridge.com  |  cn → *.longbridge.cn\n# 其余见：https://open.longbridge.com/zh-CN/docs/getting-started#环境变量\n# 夜盘行情 true/false，默认 false\n# LONGBRIDGE_ENABLE_OVERNIGHT=false\n# K 线推送 realtime 或 confirmed，默认 realtime\n# LONGBRIDGE_PUSH_CANDLESTICK_MODE=realtime\n# 连接时是否打印行情包（与 README / full-guide 一致：未设置时应用侧默认为关闭，等同 false）\n# 设为 1 / true / yes 开启 SDK 详细行情包日志（调试长桥连接时使用）\n# LONGBRIDGE_PRINT_QUOTE_PACKAGES=false\n\n# ===================================\n# AI 模型配置\n# ===================================\n# 完整说明：docs/LLM_CONFIG_GUIDE.md\n#\n# 【快速上手】填一个 API Key 即可运行，系统自动识别模型。\n#   Gemini（免费额度）→ 填 GEMINI_API_KEY\n#   DeepSeek（性价比高）→ 填 DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\n#   AIHubmix（聚合平台）→ 填 AIHUBMIX_KEY\n#\n# 【进阶】需要多模型 / 多平台 fallback → 配置下方「多渠道」或在 Web 设置页可视化管理。\n# ===================================\n\n# --- API Key（填一个即可）---\n\n# Gemini（https://aistudio.google.com）\nGEMINI_API_KEY=\n# 多 Key 负载均衡：GEMINI_API_KEYS=key1,key2,key3\n\n# DeepSeek（https://platform.deepseek.com）\n# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=\n\n# AIHubmix 聚合（https://aihubmix.com/?aff=CfMq）\n# 一个 Key 用 GPT/Claude/Gemini/GLM/Qwen 等模型，无需科学上网\n# AIHUBMIX_KEY=\n\n# Anthropic Claude（https://console.anthropic.com）\n# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=\n\n# OpenAI / 兼容 API\n# OPENAI_API_KEY=\n# OPENAI_BASE_URL=                     # 第三方 API 地址（中转站/代理），留空用官方\n\n# Ollama 本地模型（无需 API Key，推荐）\n# OLLAMA_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434\n# LITELLM_MODEL=ollama/qwen3:8b\n#\n# 或使用渠道模式：\n# LLM_CHANNELS=ollama\n# LLM_OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":34,"aggregated":"# ===================================\n# A股自选股智能分析系统 - 环境变量配置模板\n# 复制此文件为 .env 并填入真实配置\n# ===================================\n\n# 自选股列表（逗号分隔，支持沪深两市代码）\n# 沪市：600xxx, 601xxx, 603xxx\n# 深市：000xxx, 002xxx, 300xxx\nSTOCK_LIST=600519,300750,002594\n\n# 数据源配置\n# Tushare Pro Token（可选，从 https://tushare.pro/weborder/#/login?reg=834638 获取）\nTUSHARE_TOKEN=\n# TickFlow API Key（可选，用于 A 股大盘复盘指数增强；若套餐支持标的池查询，也可增强市场统计）\n# TICKFLOW_API_KEY=\n# Longbridge OpenAPI（可选，美股/港股量比、换手率、PE 等字段兜底）\n# 从 https://open.longbridge.com/ 获取\n# LONGBRIDGE_APP_KEY=\n# LONGBRIDGE_APP_SECRET=\n# LONGBRIDGE_ACCESS_TOKEN=\n# static_info 进程内缓存秒数，默认 86400；0=每次请求拉取\n# LONGBRIDGE_STATIC_INFO_TTL_SECONDS=86400\n# Longbridge SDK 语言与 REPORT_LANGUAGE（zh/en）一致；SDK 日志写入 LOG_DIR/longbridge_sdk.log\n# 接入点（与 REPORT_LANGUAGE 无关；留空则用下列默认值）：\n# LONGBRIDGE_HTTP_URL=https://openapi.longbridge.com\n# LONGBRIDGE_QUOTE_WS_URL=wss://openapi-quote.longbridge.com/v2\n# LONGBRIDGE_TRADE_WS_URL=wss://openapi-trade.longbridge.com/v2\n# LONGBRIDGE_REGION=hk\n# 覆盖接入点；SDK 内部用 LONGPORT_REGION（不带 BRIDGE）自动选择，\n# 代码会自动同步 LONGBRIDGE_REGION → LONGPORT_REGION。\n# hk → *.longbridge.com  |  cn → *.longbridge.cn\n# 其余见：https://open.longbridge.com/zh-CN/docs/getting-started#环境变量\n# 夜盘行情 true/false，默认 false\n# LONGBRIDGE_ENABLE_OVERNIGHT=false\n# K 线推送 realtime 或 confirmed，默认 realtime\n# LONGBRIDGE_PUSH_CANDLESTICK_MODE=realtime\n# 连接时是否打印行情包（与 README / full-guide 一致：未设置时应用侧默认为关闭，等同 false）\n# 设为 1 / true / yes 开启 SDK 详细行情包日志（调试长桥连接时使用）\n# LONGBRIDGE_PRINT_QUOTE_PACKAGES=false\n\n# ===================================\n# AI 模型配置\n# ===================================\n# 完整说明：docs/LLM_CONFIG_GUIDE.md\n#\n# 【快速上手】填一个 API Key 即可运行，系统自动识别模型。\n#   Gemini（免费额度）→ 填 GEMINI_API_KEY\n#   DeepSeek（性价比高）→ 填 DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\n#   AIHubmix（聚合平台）→ 填 AIHUBMIX_KEY\n#\n# 【进阶】需要多模型 / 多平台 fallback → 配置下方「多渠道」或在 Web 设置页可视化管理。\n# ===================================\n\n# --- API Key（填一个即可）---\n\n# Gemini（https://aistudio.google.com）\nGEMINI_API_KEY=\n# 多 Key 负载均衡：GEMINI_API_KEYS=key1,key2,key3\n\n# DeepSeek（https://platform.deepseek.com）\n# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=\n\n# AIHubmix 聚合（https://aihubmix.com/?aff=CfMq）\n# 一个 Key 用 GPT/Claude/Gemini/GLM/Qwen 等模型，无需科学上网\n# AIHUBMIX_KEY=\n\n# Anthropic Claude（https://console.anthropic.com）\n# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=\n\n# OpenAI / 兼容 API\n# OPENAI_API_KEY=\n# OPENAI_BASE_URL=                     # 第三方 API 地址（中转站/代理），留空用官方\n\n# Ollama 本地模型（无需 API Key，推荐）\n# OLLAMA_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434\n# LITELLM_MODEL=ollama/qwen3:8b\n#\n# 或使用渠道模式：\n# LLM_CHANNELS=ollama\n# LLM_OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777102965471}}
{"type":"message","id":"6593ec02","parentId":"f05ecfa9","timestamp":"2026-04-25T07:42:53.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check what's the overall plan here. The user wants a standalone desktop version of this repo. Since electron is not installed globally, I need to install it. Let me check if there's a way to install it.\n\nActually looking at the build script, it uses `npx electron-builder` from within the `apps/dsa-desktop` directory after `npm install`. So the electron is a local dependency, not global.\n\nThe key issue is:\n1. `electron` is not found globally\n2. But it can be installed locally via npm in the dsa-desktop directory\n\nLet me check what's needed and plan the configuration. I'll install electron via npm in the desktop app directory.\n\nBut wait - the user said this repo is already integrated into their quant system. They want a \"单独配置一个桌面版\". So they want a separate deployment of just the desktop app, pointing to the same data or with its own config.\n \nI think what they're really asking for is to set up a desktop app that can run independently, separate from their main quant system. I should clarify what they need in terms of configuration, then proceed with installing electron locally and setting up the backend before building the app.\n\nLet me first check if there's already a `dist/backend/stock_analysis` directory or if I need to build one, and confirm what Python dependencies are required for the backend build to work.","thinkingSignature":"62091b2ecb2ed3e310d9aa6f25c90897a98fd52034e798a06adc53c0630ab6d4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_usmorugsmjuz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/dist/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"dist dir not found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":999,"output":335,"cacheRead":62176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63510,"cost":