{"type":"message","id":"95334734","parentId":"a6307da2","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:05:47.562Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-25 16:05:43 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b51f313bb84acc10273ac85d94e5]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51f313bb84acc10273ac85d94e5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 16:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n通知渠道就是飞书啊，能不能用minimax的api key？"}],"timestamp":1777104347552}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9ab3b8f","parentId":"95334734","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:05:55.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to use Feishu (飞书) as the notification channel and wants to use MiniMax API key. Let me check if MiniMax is supported as an LLM in this system.\n\nLooking at the .env.example, MiniMax is listed under search engine configuration:\n```\n# MiniMax API Key（Coding Plan Web Search，支持多个，逗号分隔）\n# 获取: https://platform.minimaxi.com/\n# MINIMAX_API_KEYS=your_minimax_key_here\n```\n\nHowever, for AI model (LLM) usage, MiniMax is NOT listed as a supported model. The supported models are:\n\n\n- Gemini (free tier)\n- DeepSeek\n- AIHubmix (aggregation platform)\n- Anthropic Claude\n- OpenAI compatible API\n- Ollama local models\n\nSo MiniMax can only be used for web search, not as an LLM. But the user asked if they can use the MiniMax API key for this. They probably want to use MiniMax as the AI model for analysis, but MiniMax isn't currently supported as an LLM option in the system. I should let them know that MiniMax is only available for search functionality and suggest alternatives if they want to use it for AI analysis.","thinkingSignature":"1e3eb9e2ca22b3bf5162585703d09314d5e554c46945b0b95908b87de1e7981f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMiniMax 可以用作**搜索/舆情**（`MINIMAX_API_KEYS`），但不能用作 AI 分析模型。\n\n系统支持的分析模型是这些：\n- ✅ Gemini（免费额度，推荐）\n- ✅ DeepSeek\n- ✅ AIHubmix（一 Key 打通 GPT/Claude/Gemini/GLM）\n- ✅ Anthropic Claude\n- ✅ OpenAI 兼容 API（含第三方中转）\n\n如果你有 MiniMax 的 API Key，建议直接换成 **AIHubmix**，因为 AIHubmix 聚合平台自带 MiniMax 模型，而且一个 Key 就能用全球主流模型，不用额外配置。\n\n需要我帮你基于 AIHubmix 写一版精简配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":313,"output":393,"cacheRead":84544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85250,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777104347572,"responseId":"063ba8ddacb627d00eda8e8d2c2cadb1"}}
