{"type":"message","id":"78fab25d","parentId":"2da9e9ef","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:06:32.107Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-25 16:06:30 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b51f32e9114b4c4fd75f3c3363fc]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51f32e9114b4c4fd75f3c3363fc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 16:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n我已经购买了minimax的coding plan了"}],"timestamp":1777104392098}}
{"type":"message","id":"37a61747","parentId":"78fab25d","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:06:41.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has a MiniMax coding plan. MiniMax's API can be used as a search/舆情 engine in this system, but not as the main LLM analysis model. However, wait - MiniMax does have models. Let me think about this more carefully.\n\nLooking at the `.env.example` in the project, I don't see a direct MiniMax LLM model configuration. The project uses LiteLLM which supports many providers. MiniMax does have an API that could potentially work through OpenAI-compatible endpoint.\n\nActually, wait - MiniMax does offer API access to their models. Let me check what MiniMax's API looks like. \n\nI'm trying to figure out whether MiniMax actually provides LLM API access or if they're primarily a platform for other models like GPT-4. Since the project supports OpenAI-compatible APIs, I could potentially configure MiniMax as a custom endpoint if they offer one, but I don't have reliable information about their specific API format.\n","thinkingSignature":"b997755c2918e2fa5eaf79443cb8a7b1968be35d441b43a697a3eb115672a871"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMiniMax Coding Plan 有 API Key 的话，可以配置在**飞书搜索**和**分析模型**两个地方：\n\n**1. 飞书搜索用（MINIMAX_API_KEYS）：**\n系统已经支持 MiniMax 搜索，这是最直接的用法。\n\n**2. 作为 AI 分析模型（LLM）：**\n需要确认你的 MiniMax API 是否支持 OpenAI 兼容格式。如果支持，可以这样配：\n\n```env\nLLM_CHANNELS=minimax\nLLM_MINIMAX_BASE_URL=https://api.minimax.chat/v1\nLLM_MINIMAX_API_KEY=你的key\nLLM_MINIMAX_MODELS=...（看API文档）\n```\n\n你知道你的 MiniMax API Key 对应的 API 地址和模型名是什么吗？或者你知道 MiniMax 的 API 文档链接？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":440,"output":363,"cacheRead":84832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85635,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777104392119,"responseId":"063ba9092f35fd6e65ae37070c650dc1"}}
