{"type":"message","id":"29a28a6c","parentId":"494a072b","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:06:46.569Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-25 16:06:44 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b51f32f85dca4c1496d36a360bb7]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51f32f85dca4c1496d36a360bb7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 16:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n我本地部署的deepseek 行不行"}],"timestamp":1777104406558}}
{"type":"message","id":"523c9e3f","parentId":"29a28a6c","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:06:55.417Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they can use a locally deployed DeepSeek model. Let me think about what they need to configure.\n\nFor local DeepSeek (Ollama or similar), they would need:\n1. OLLAMA_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434\n2. LITELLM_MODEL=ollama/deepseek-r1:7b (or whatever model name they have)\n\nBut wait - this is for the desktop app. The desktop app runs a FastAPI backend that needs to make LLM calls. If they're running DeepSeek locally via Ollama, the app can call it.\n\nHowever, there might be an issue - if their local DeepSeek is running via Ollama, it would be at localhost:11434. But the desktop app's backend also runs locally... Let me think about whether this would work.\n\n\nActually, since the desktop backend spawns locally, it can definitely reach localhost endpoints. So they can set up Ollama with their DeepSeek model and configure the desktop app to point to http://localhost:11434, or use a litellm config if they want more flexibility. The key question is whether they're using Ollama directly or another local LLM setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"171b6ba3bb9f6d408528ab83ff8eede67a727337dd2b7b04ea16be7e41bc0f46"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n本地部署的 DeepSeek 完全可以用！只要它支持 OpenAI 兼容格式。\n\n**最简单的方式（用 Ollama）：**\n\n如果你用 Ollama 跑 DeepSeek，配置 `.env`：\n\n```env\nOLLAMA_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434\nLITELLM_MODEL=ollama/deepseek-r1:7b\n```\n\n或者你的模型名不是 `deepseek-r1:7b`，告诉我具体名称。\n\n**如果用的是其他 DeepSeek 部署方式（非 Ollama）：**\n\n```env\nLLM_CHANNELS=deepseek_local\nLLM_DEEPSEEK_LOCAL_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1\nLLM_DEEPSEEK_LOCAL_API_KEY=不需要key（本地）\nLLM_DEEPSEEK_LOCAL_MODELS=你的模型名\nLITELLM_MODEL=openai/deepseek_local\n```\n\n你现在本地 DeepSeek 用的是什么方式跑的？Ollama 还是别的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":464,"output":436,"cacheRead":85248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86148,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777104406582,"responseId":"063ba9187dc781235d4914072fe4bf08"}}
