{"type":"message","id":"bde1cd56","parentId":"ebde2ffb","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:21:26.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can help configure the Feishu Webhook. This means they want to set up a Feishu webhook URL so the desktop app can send notifications to their Feishu group. Let me ask them for the webhook URL, or help them create one.\n\nTo create a Feishu webhook, they need to:\n1. Go to a Feishu group\n2. Settings -> Group Bots -> Add Bot -> Custom Bot\n3. Get the webhook URL\n\nLet me ask them if they have a webhook URL already, or if they need help setting it up.","thinkingSignature":"68c0c6bf0ab2bd22c6ff7578b13f07f43e00eb26ee975f354463af99a890e4f6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n飞书 Webhook 需要你自己在飞书群里创建，拿到 URL 后我帮你填进去。\n\n**创建步骤：**\n1. 打开飞书 → 进入目标群\n2. 点群设置（右上角 `...`）→ **群机器人** → 添加机器人 → **自定义机器人**\n3. 设置名字（随便填）→ 复制 Webhook 地址\n\nWebhook URL 格式类似：\n```\nhttps://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/xxxxxxxxxxxx\n```\n\n拿到 URL 后发给我，我帮你配置到桌面版的 `.env` 里。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102,"output":244,"cacheRead":94592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94938,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777105276956,"responseId":"063bac7e3549635631ebb41c51b4d232"}}
