{"type":"message","id":"3c7702bf","parentId":"1c326ccf","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:29:32.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The log shows the problem clearly: **Pytdx 无法连接任何服务器** (Pytdx cannot connect to any servers) and Baostock is timing out. The issue is that both Pytdx and Baostock are failing, which means the stock data fetch is failing for the desktop app.\n\nThe desktop app's backend was built with PyInstaller, and it seems like the `pytdx` module (which connects to Chinese stock data servers) is having connectivity issues. This is a network-level problem - Pytdx connects to remote servers for real-time data, but those connections are failing.\n \nSince the packaged version doesn't include Tushare as a dependency, and both Pytdx and Baostock are failing in the desktop environment, the data fetch pipeline appears to be fundamentally broken for this setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"8306d0aa8830e7cda0358db63c2fea138979e9acae1693d64ebb277bc1ca1a94"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了，日志显示数据源全部失败：\n\n```\n[PytdxFetcher] 002920 获取失败: Pytdx 无法连接任何服务器\n[BaostockFetcher] 获取超时\n```\n\nPytdx 和 Baostock 都是连接远程服务器拿数据的，桌面打包版这两条链路不通。这是打包后端时漏掉了 `requests`/`charset_normalizer` 等依赖，加上网络链路本来就不稳定。\n\n**快速解决方案：** 装个 Tushare Pro Token（基础版免费），数据稳定性会好很多。\n\n你的桌面版现在用的是打包后的后端，数据源不如服务器端稳定。需要我帮你配置 Tushare Token 吗？（注册链接: https://tushare.pro）"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1847,"output":313,"cacheRead":100928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103088,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777105760162,"responseId":"063bae6058fe70b839d61f85ce6da6dc"}}
