{"type":"message","id":"7104f12d","parentId":"53c31f5b","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:35:34.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error is clear now: `MiniMaxSearchProvider._record_error() takes 2 positional arguments but 3 were given` - there's a bug in the MiniMax search provider in the packaged backend. It seems like the packaged version has an incompatible version of the MiniMax search provider code.\n\nThe issue is that the packaged backend has an older/different version of the MiniMax search provider that doesn't match the data fetching code. This is a code incompatibility issue in the packaged build.\n\nLet me check what version of the MiniMax API is being used and whether we can fix this. The problem is that the `api` module IS now included (since we rebuilt with all the hidden imports), but the `MiniMaxSearchProvider._record_error()` signature changed between the source code and what's packaged.\n \nThe real issue is likely that our PyInstaller build bundled a different version of the MiniMax code than what's actually in the main.py we're running. The packaged `stock_analysis` executable is using its own internal versions of these modules, so there's a mismatch between what main.py expects and what got packaged. Since MiniMax is only used for search and efinance is handling the stock list data fine, the simplest fix would be to just disable the MiniMax search provider in the .env configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"328a141328af410e4c67a4064601aa1ad27d59ebfb835c179e1c1221bfaa4399"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n找到了！是 MiniMax 搜索模块的 bug——打包后的后端里 `MiniMaxSearchProvider._record_error()` 方法签名对不上，调用时多传了一个参数。这是打包时模块版本和源码不匹配导致的。\n\n**两个解决方向：**\n\n**方案1（推荐）：** 先禁掉 MiniMax 搜索，让系统用其他搜索源，股票分析就能跑通\n\n**方案2：** 重新做一个完整一致的后端打包（需要一点时间）\n\n你想先用方案1快速让分析跑起来，还是等方案2彻底修好？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":481,"output":377,"cacheRead":103392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104250,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777106126316,"responseId":"063bafce2c329ab3cf977111f1729d97"}}
