{"type":"compaction","id":"6edd7c3e","parentId":"e07b222a","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:59:47.159Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Set up a standalone macOS desktop edition of the ZhuLinsen/daily_stock_analysis repo (already integrated into user's quant system)\n- Along the way: disable non-trading-day cron pushes, fix cron schedules, install dependencies, build the Electron DMG\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Non-trading days should not trigger push notifications → convert daily crons to weekday-only (1-5)\n- User prefers MiniMax API (already purchased Coding Plan) for both AI analysis model and notification/search\n- Notification channel: Feishu (飞书)\n- User does NOT have AIHubmix or Gemini keys; wants to use MiniMax directly if possible\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Identified which cron tasks run on weekends without weekday restriction\n- [x] Deleted daily post-market audit cron (id: `9c120016-bb26-4799-9b40-4580caefaa29`) per user request\n- [x] Updated `08:50全球股市早间要闻` cron (id: `71b19e21-52a4-446a-bc53-72399efd63f1`) to weekday-only: `50 8 * * 1-5`\n- [x] Updated `21:00来福投研会-夜间值班` cron (id: `investment-research-background-overnight-2100`) to weekday-only: `0 21 * * 1-5`\n- [x] Identified other crons already on `1-5` schedule (no action needed)\n- [x] Cloned/detected existing daily_stock_analysis repo at `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/`\n- [x] Read repo structure, CLAUDE.md, README.md, desktop packaging docs, build scripts\n- [x] Installed npm dependencies for `apps/dsa-desktop/` (electron ~80MB)\n- [x] Installed npm dependencies for `apps/dsa-web/`\n- [x] Built React UI via `npm run build` → output to `static/`\n- [x] Built Python backend via PyInstaller → output to `dist/stock_analysis/`\n- [x] Copied backend binary to `dist/backend/stock_analysis/stock_analysis`\n- [x] Built macOS Electron DMG: `dist/Daily Stock Analysis-3.12.0-arm64.dmg` (485MB)\n- [x] Opened the DMG in Finder for the user\n- [x] Created config template: `apps/dsa-desktop/.env.desktop.template` with essential settings\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] User needs to configure the `.env` with their API key and stock list\n- [ ] User wants to use MiniMax API as the LLM model — unconfirmed if MiniMax is supported as analysis model in this system\n\n### Blocked\n- MiniMax is only listed for search (`MINIMAX_API_KEYS`), not as an LLM analysis model — needs verification of OpenAI-compatible endpoint\n- User has MiniMax Coding Plan but may need alternative LLM provider (DeepSeek/AIHubmix/Gemini)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Use open (Finder) to mount DMG for user**: DMG opened via `open` command\n- **Desktop build successful on macOS arm64**: Built DMG, user can drag to Applications\n- **Config template created separately**: `env.desktop.template` — clean minimal version\n- **Cron tasks restricted to weekdays**: `1-5` suffix applied to both morning news and night research tasks\n\n## Pending User Questions\n- Does MiniMax offer an OpenAI-compatible LLM API endpoint? If yes, what is the base URL and model name?\n- User has purchased MiniMax Coding Plan — can MiniMax be used as the LLM in the desktop app?\n- User wants to use Feishu (飞书) as notification channel\n\n## Exact Identifiers\n- Repo path: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/`\n- Desktop app path: `apps/dsa-desktop/`\n- Web app path: `apps/dsa-web/`\n- Config template: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/.env.desktop.template`\n- Built DMG: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/dist/Daily Stock Analysis-3.12.0-arm64.dmg`\n- Backend binary: `dist/backend/stock_analysis/stock_analysis`\n- Main.js: `apps/dsa-desktop/main.js`\n- Build script: `scripts/build-desktop-macos.sh`\n- Backend build script: `scripts/build-backend-macos.sh`\n- Cron IDs:\n  - Deleted post-market audit: `9c120016-bb26-4799-9b40-4580caefaa29`\n  - Morning news (updated): `71b19e21-52a4-446a-bc53-72399efd63f1` → `50 8 * * 1-5`\n  - Night research (updated): `investment-research-background-overnight-2100` → `0 21 * * 1-5`\n- User: 张玲, sender_id: `ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae`\n- Message IDs: `om_x100b51f23f2e4194b4861d4827a00a0`, `om_x100b51f293d0cc80c35da2c2a8402ad`, `om_x100b51f290aa94a4c2c237cca706529`, `om_x100b51f2ab4f7130b2cbac1b31c8a55`, `om_x100b51f2b4bcacacc4570a2a1eca14f`, `om_x100b51f2b32f58a0c457b687a7c9544`, `om_x100b51f31e2fa0b4c2a8a0e1d96e230`, `om_x100b51f31af6d8b4c3892c07ee5f4e2`, `om_x100b51f313bb84acc10273ac85d94e5`, `om_x100b51f32e9114b4c4fd75f3c3363fc`\n- Runtime info: model=`minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7`, default_model=`beecode/gpt-5.4`\n- Platform: macOS Darwin arm64, Python 3.14.3, Node.js v24.14.0, npm available\n- OS: 25.4.0\n- Electron: v31.7.7 (downloaded for build)\n- electron-builder: v24.13.3\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## 目标\n自动化完成桌面应用的环境配置（复制模板到正确位置、启动 Ollama 服务）。\n\n## 进度\n### 完成\n- [x] 已将 `.env.desktop.template` 复制到桌面 `/Users/ling/Desktop/.env.desktop.template`\n\n### 进行中\n- [ ] 将模板内容复制到桌面应用的最终 `.env` 文件位置\n- [ ] 确保 Ollama 服务在后台运行（`ollama serve`）\n\n### 阻塞\n- 桌面应用尚未安装（仅挂载了 DMG），无法直接写入 `/Applications/` 下的最终 `.env` 位置；需等待用户完成安装后再复制。\n\n## 关键路径 & 标识符\n- 模板源路径：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/.env.desktop.template`\n- 桌面应用期望 `.env` 位置：与 `.app` bundle 同级目录（通常为 `/Applications/`）\n- 用户：张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\n- 时间戳：2026-04-25 16:09 GMT+8\n- 消息 ID：om_x100b51f3253564b8c10337b431c38c4（当前消息），om_x100b51f3265c40a4b2dae8e872609fb（被回复消息）\n- 平台：飞书 DM\n\n## 待办\n1. 等待用户完成桌面应用安装（从 DMG 拖到 `/Applications/`）\n2. 将模板内容复制到应用目录下的 `.env` 文件\n3. 启动 Ollama 服务（`ollama serve`）\n\n## 待响应用户提问\n用户问：“这些事你不能帮我做？”——即要求 AI 代为完成复制模板和启动 Ollama 的操作。AI 已开始执行（复制到桌面），但最终位置复制和 Ollama 启动尚未完成。需后续继续处理。\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-04-25 16:06:44 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b51f32f85dca4c1496d36a360bb7]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51f32f85dca4c1496d36a360bb7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 16:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n我本地部署的deepseek 行不行\n- Assistant: 本地部署的 DeepSeek 完全可以用！只要它支持 OpenAI 兼容格式。\n\n**最简单的方式（用 Ollama）：**\n\n如果你用 Ollama 跑 DeepSeek，配置 `.env`：\n\n```env\nOLLAMA_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434\nLITELLM_MODEL=ollama/deepseek-r1:7b\n```\n\n或者你的模型名不是 `deepseek-r1:7b`，告诉我具体名称。\n\n**如果用的是其他 DeepSeek 部署方式（非 Ollama）：**\n\n```env\nLLM_CHANNELS=deepseek_local\nLLM_DEEPSEEK_LOCAL_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1\nLLM_DEEPSEEK_LOCAL_API_KEY=不需要key（本地）\nLLM_DEEPSEEK_LOCAL_MODELS=你的模型名\nLITELLM_MODEL=openai/deepseek_local\n```\n\n你现在本地 DeepSeek 用的是什么方式跑的？Ollama 还是别的？\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: System: [2026-04-25 16:07:11 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b51f32c3bacbcc42dd401175662f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51f32c3bacbcc42dd401175662f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 16:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nollama,你帮我配置吧\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): deepseek-r1:14b            c333b7232bdb    9.0 GB    7 days ago\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (edit): Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/.env.desktop.template.\n- Assistant: 配置好了，本地 DeepSeek R1 14B：\n\n```env\nOLLAMA_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434\nLITELLM_MODEL=ollama/deepseek-r1:14b\n```\n\n同时 MiniMax API Key 填进去可以加强新闻搜索。\n\n桌面版 DMG 已经就绪，安装后编辑 `.env` 就能用了。\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: System: [2026-04-25 16:08:20 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b51f32989b8b0c33015d766b4418]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51f32989b8b0c33015d766b4418\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 16:08 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nminimax api key：sk-api-GFIXa5ytosSMOfmYr5aJ7Yc3RzjkIOBjajKPydtX...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (edit): Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/.env.desktop.template.\n- Assistant: 已写入配置模板。\n\n**提醒：API Key 现在保存在桌面端的配置模板文件里**，`.env.desktop.template` 路径是：\n\n```\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/.env.desktop.template\n```\n\n如果你希望桌面版运行时用这个模板自动生成 `.env`，安装后首次启动前需要手动把模板内容复制过去，或者安装后 app 会在同目录生成 `.env`，你再把模板内容粘贴进去填好。\n\n要用这个 Key 跑分析的话，记得确保 Ollama 服务在后台运行（`ollama serve`）。\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/CLAUDE.md\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/README.md\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/main.js\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/apps/dsa-desktop/package.json\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/docs/desktop-package.md\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspac